Second pack for ponis jail new maps

Maps:
ba_island_jail_b1.bsp
ba_jail_antediem.bsp
ba_jail_blackhawk_v4_fix.bsp
ba_jail_escape_v2.bsp
ba_jail_jk_v1_fixed.bsp
Ba_Jail_KAJOLY1_FIX1.bsp

After you download this pack you need to unpack the .rar file. After you have unpacked it you need to move all files in your maps folder. 
You find maps folder in : C/D/E -> program files -> steam -> steamapps -> ''your name'' -> counter-strike -> cstrike -> maps
